<item>
            <title>[LU-14032] The agent inode under directory with S_ISGID causes group quota discrepancy</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14032</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If the parent directory is set as S_ISGID, the agent inode for the remote stripe directory&lt;br/&gt;
under it will be created with its GID as its parent GID during creation, but it is restore as&lt;br/&gt;
current_fsgid() after the creation, which cause the group quota discrepancy.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
